follow-science is structurally inspired by:

  zarazhangrui/follow-builders
  https://github.com/zarazhangrui/follow-builders

follow-science is a new skill focused on configurable scientific research
signals rather than AI builder social/media updates. It uses public scholarly
metadata sources and user-provided profiles to prepare evidence for an AI agent
to write an editorial-style research brief.

Do not commit runtime secrets, personal email addresses, local profiles, or
private research notes.
